{"article_url": "https://www.xinli001.com/info/100411920", "image": "https://ossimg.xinli001.com/20181023/fc4e2773ac4a8892c4d2fe87308f48f1.jpeg!120x120", "title": "错过支付宝锦鲤不怕，但别错过这篇文章", "describe": "学习不是比谁睡得少，秃得早，也不是搞虚假努力的自我感动。它跟开车一样，讲究的是技巧和方法。", "author": "YouCore", "push_time": " 2018-10-22 ", "count": "2117阅读", "tag": ["习惯养成", "学习技巧", "时间与效率"], "like": ["1赞"], "article_detail": ["\n                    <div class=\"cover-con\">\n                        <img class=\"article-cover\" src=\"https://ossimg.xinli001.com/20181023/fc4e2773ac4a8892c4d2fe87308f48f1.jpeg?x-oss-process=image/quality,Q_80\" alt=\"文章封面\">\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"yxl-editor\">\n                        <div class=\"yxl-editor-article \">\n                                                                <h6><span style=\"\">作者 / 苗小小</span></h6><p><span style=\"\"><br/></span></p><p>今天这篇文章是YouCore的读者所写。</p><p><br/></p><p>一篇有趣、有料、有感情的读书笔记，小编不得不从她的公众号转过来。</p><p><br/></p><p><img src=\"https://ossimg.xinli001.com/20181023/f75ff42683f1e2dc2cadde1e7e7206f0.jpeg?x-oss-process=image/quality,Q_80\"/><span style=\"\"></span></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em style=\"\"><span style=\"\"></span></em></strong><img src=\"https://ossimg.xinli001.com/20181023/0dc8a5f6498463694818186ec2a4ed52.png?x-oss-process=image/quality,Q_80\"/><strong><em style=\"\"><span style=\"\">01</span></em></strong></h1><p> </p><p><span style=\"\"> </span></p><p><span style=\"\">每当听到有人说自己年阅读量在200本以上时，我都急得头秃！</span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"\">像我这种对自己有要求的人，是不会允许自己落后别人太多的。</span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"\">于是，我四处攒书——纸质书、Kindle电子书、PDF，只要能找到的我都收藏了。</span></p><p><br/></p><p><strong><span style=\"\">我还给自己定了一个雄心勃勃的读书计划，每天至少要阅读20页</span></strong><span style=\"\">。</span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"\">理想是丰满的，但是现实却是相当骨感——大部分书我都只“翻阅”了1%到40%：</span></p><p><br/></p><blockquote><p>《高效能人士的七个习惯》至今还卡在第二个习惯 ；</p><p><br/></p><p>《少有人走的路》还停留在P106；</p><p><br/></p><p>《自控力》更惨，才翻了第一篇章，因为我实在控制不住自己去干点别的。</p></blockquote><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"\">不过，我也算“成功”地达成了一半的目标——<strong style=\"\">翻过的书超过了200本</strong>。</span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"\">但得不偿失的是，焦虑也增加了200倍，因为有200多本没看完的书等着我去看。</span></p><p><span style=\"\"> </span><br/></p><p> </p><h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"\"><em style=\"\"><span style=\"\"></span></em></span></strong><img src=\"https://ossimg.xinli001.com/20181023/60d30d2594640faabd09e066d7c925a4.png?x-oss-process=image/quality,Q_80\"/><strong><span style=\"\"><em style=\"\"><span style=\"\">02</span></em></span></strong></h1><p> </p><p> </p><p><span style=\"\">我本以为我这辈子就要这么一直焦虑下去了。</span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"\">可这一切，随着一篇文章全都烟消云散了。</span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">看了这篇文章，我醍醐灌顶：<strong style=\"\">原来我只是为看书而看书，完全没有目的</strong>。</span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"\">这就是为啥我什么书都看不完，即使看完了也没啥用的万恶之源。</span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"\">于是，我试着用里面的多重阅读法读了一本《小说课》，破天荒地第一次读完了全书，不仅如此，我还用<span style=\"\">《小说课》</span>里教的方法，写了一篇文章。</span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"\">当时，我觉得全身的细胞都兴奋得在发抖——我挖到宝啦！</span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"\">于是，我从自己写作母婴文的目的出发，一发不可收拾地看了</span><span style=\"\">《小故事》、《救猫咪——电影编剧宝典》、《儿童发展心理学》</span><span style=\"\">等10多本书。</span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"\">现在，我也可以像别人官宣那样高调地说一句：</span></p><p><span style=\"\"><br/></span></p><p><strong style=\"\"><span style=\"\">以前那个毫无章法的我死了，现在请叫我：钮轱辘*读书狂。</span></strong></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"\">让我如此膨胀的那篇文章，就是YouCore公众号2018年4月5日发的<a style=\"\" href=\"http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIxODU0NzA0MQ==&mid=2247486889&idx=1&sn=c931d2dac337cd4ad576b1e3465ecf17&chksm=97e99ba7a09e12b1db58b0e3814f88ec4063f1241f5b0f3265d43e1eb47ae1a75ac9105dd79c&scene=21#wechat_redirect\" target=\"_blank\">《推荐！比高效阅读更高效的三大阅读法》</a></span></p><p><span style=\"\"><br/></span></p><p><img style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: 592px !important; visibility: visible !important;\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/xye473fPuibyWA0OtYRmpQZCcBYpNDqjg4TAlIMgym7XU1OTNwEwZyGuAqI7TEvwHBHsvPgB2R2SdLd9mT9rgag/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" data-copyright=\"0\" data-ratio=\"0.30465666929755325\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/xye473fPuibyWA0OtYRmpQZCcBYpNDqjg4TAlIMgym7XU1OTNwEwZyGuAqI7TEvwHBHsvPgB2R2SdLd9mT9rgag/640?wx_fmt=png\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1267\" _width=\"592px\" data-fail=\"0\" data-local=\"false\"/></p><p><span style=\"\">▲ 喏，就是这一篇</span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"\">因为这篇文章对我如此有效，因此我又顺藤摸瓜地找了下面这本《学习力：颠覆职场学习的高效方法》</span><span style=\"\">（我看的文章就节选自这本书）</span><span style=\"\">。</span></p><p><span style=\"\"><br/></span></p><p><img style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: 342px !important; visibility: visible !important;\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/xye473fPuibyWA0OtYRmpQZCcBYpNDqjgprvKxPzKmsw2vb0PeqCIkbbxUVBXg812jrZ1nL3HgrHkhSriartNFdw/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" data-copyright=\"0\" data-ratio=\"1.386\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/xye473fPuibyWA0OtYRmpQZCcBYpNDqjgprvKxPzKmsw2vb0PeqCIkbbxUVBXg812jrZ1nL3HgrHkhSriartNFdw/640?wx_fmt=png\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"500\" _width=\"342px\" data-fail=\"0\" data-local=\"false\"/></p><p><span style=\"\"></span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"\">一口气花了6个多小时，用手机看完了这本书的在线阅读版，将我的一双杏桃大眼都看成一条缝的丹凤眼了。</span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"\">虽然视力受损了，但我还是觉得很值！</span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"\">因为学习的书，虽然市面上有很多，但真要找到一本将学习这件小事讲通讲透，又能落地的好书，就跟支付宝锦鲤一样，全凭运气！</span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"\">能碰到《学习力》，真是我今年最大的运气！</span></p><p><span style=\"\"><br/></span></p><p><img style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: 286px !important; visibility: visible !important;\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/xye473fPuibyWA0OtYRmpQZCcBYpNDqjgvOcRx9umW4HE77Q0BodeTQmnuYHpH4zEQnMXoegTlfTEgtAzicibNR5w/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" data-copyright=\"0\" data-ratio=\"1.2188755020080322\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/xye473fPuibyWA0OtYRmpQZCcBYpNDqjgvOcRx9umW4HE77Q0BodeTQmnuYHpH4zEQnMXoegTlfTEgtAzicibNR5w/640?wx_fmt=png\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"498\" _width=\"286px\" data-fail=\"0\" data-local=\"false\"/></p><p><span style=\"\"></span>  <br/></p><h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"\"><em style=\"\"><span style=\"\"></span></em></span></strong><img src=\"https://ossimg.xinli001.com/20181023/59f9de20f1c30e9c45b5bdd7901ff080.png?x-oss-process=image/quality,Q_80\"/><strong><span style=\"\"><em style=\"\"><span style=\"\">03</span></em></span></strong></h1><p> </p><p> </p><p><span style=\"\">别看《学习力：颠覆职场学习的高效方法》这个书名，一本正经，一股子老干部范儿，<strong style=\"\">但它的内核有料又有趣，真正做到了“深入”又“浅出”。</strong></span></p><p><br/></p><blockquote><p><span style=\"\">书里说，人的大脑是一个有缺陷且忘性大的容器，要想效率最高，就要充分运用3大学习策略：</span></p><p><span style=\"\"><br/></span></p><p><strong style=\"\"><span style=\"\">① <span class=\"Apple-converted-space\" style=\"\"> </span></span></strong><span style=\"\">功利性学习； </span></p><p><strong style=\"\"><span style=\"\">② <span class=\"Apple-converted-space\" style=\"\"> </span></span></strong><span style=\"\">搭好知识框架；</span></p><p><strong style=\"\"><span style=\"\">③ <span class=\"Apple-converted-space\" style=\"\"> </span></span></strong><span style=\"\">做到可迁移。</span></p></blockquote><p><br/></p><p><strong style=\"\"><span style=\"\">简单说，就是带着目的性学习，搭建和完善好自己的知识体系，做到可以在任意平台迁移。</span></strong></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"\">除了上面的3大学习策略，书里还给了5类上手即用的学习技巧，以及各类技能学习的应用演示，真正让你学得会，学得快，而且学得牢。</span></p><p><br/></p><p><strong style=\"\"><span style=\"\">多重阅读法就是充分融入了3大学习策略、5类学习技巧的一种高效阅读方法。</span></strong></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"\">在这个方法指导下，我可以3个小时就翻完一本P244的《小说课》，并将内容打散融进自己搭建的个人知识体系中。</span></p><p><span style=\"\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"\">同时，学以致用，输出了相关读书笔记及文章。</span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"\">也可以2个半小时看完一本200多页的《儿童发展心理学》，并在充分吸收书中内容的基础上完成了一篇关于延迟满足的稿子，同时还将相关内容沉淀到自己的个人知识体系中</span><span style=\"\">（看我傲娇的眼神）</span><span style=\"\">。</span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"\">以前，看这种类型的书，可能范冰冰罚款都交清了，我序言还没看完。</span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"\">在遇到《学习力》之前，我完全没有搭建个人知识体系的意识，读书也是兴之所至、率性而为。</span></p><p><span style=\"\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"\">我行走江湖，主要靠的是自己喷薄的才华和时有时无的记忆力</span><span style=\"\">（似乎有点悲伤）</span><span style=\"\">。</span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"\">但看过《学习力》后，我就完全不同啦。</span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"\">下面以我阅读《小说课》为例，来看看钮轱辘*读书狂是怎么上线的。</span></p><p><span style=\"\"><br/></span></p><p><img style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: 252px !important; visibility: visible !important;\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/xye473fPuibyWA0OtYRmpQZCcBYpNDqjgKSnWJ0NozKxtOOu5KIHjvRLU4jtic0Fo2I3Xfn4LdbGH81o7PVpWiaTg/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" data-copyright=\"0\" data-ratio=\"0.8987341772151899\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/xye473fPuibyWA0OtYRmpQZCcBYpNDqjgKSnWJ0NozKxtOOu5KIHjvRLU4jtic0Fo2I3Xfn4LdbGH81o7PVpWiaTg/640?wx_fmt=png\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"316\" _width=\"252px\" data-fail=\"0\" data-local=\"false\"/></p><p> <strong> </strong></p><h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"\"><em style=\"\"><span style=\"\"></span></em></span></strong><img src=\"https://ossimg.xinli001.com/20181023/3732f47844ed70c8ba4720673e71370f.png?x-oss-process=image/quality,Q_80\"/><strong><span style=\"\"><em style=\"\"><span style=\"\">04</span></em></span></strong></h1><h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong> </strong></h1><p> </p><p><span style=\"\"><strong style=\"\"><span style=\"\">▼ 第一步，阅读前我定了一个明确的目的。</span></strong></span></p><p><span style=\"\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">通过了解小说的写作方法，来让自己的文章变得更具趣味性，这样才配得上自己有趣的灵魂。</span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"\">所以，《小说课》会比书架上绝大部分书更能满足这种诉求。同时，因为我要赶在3天内写一篇故事出来，从小写故事就稀烂的我，不得不看完这本书。</span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"\"><strong style=\"\"><span style=\"\"><strong style=\"\"><span style=\"\">▼ 第二步，<strong style=\"\"><span style=\"\">画一个大致的阅读框架</span></strong></span></strong></span></strong></span></p><p><strong style=\"\"><span style=\"\"><br/></span></strong></p><p><span style=\"\">在浏览完腰封，序言和目录后，我画了一个大致的阅读框架。</span></p><p><strong style=\"\"><span style=\"\"><br/></span></strong></p><p><img style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: 592px !important; visibility: visible !important;\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/xye473fPuibyWA0OtYRmpQZCcBYpNDqjgEB59p6VM292ibImG317WAGEDwA95oTrSfw4yTW5ibW9hcicJYDFn4bOIQ/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" data-copyright=\"0\" data-ratio=\"0.44359626802374896\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/xye473fPuibyWA0OtYRmpQZCcBYpNDqjgEB59p6VM292ibImG317WAGEDwA95oTrSfw4yTW5ibW9hcicJYDFn4bOIQ/640?wx_fmt=png\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1179\" _width=\"592px\" data-fail=\"0\" data-local=\"false\"/></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"\">因为《学习力》强调读书时要带入自己原先的经验，因此这个框架并不是书的目录，而是结合我已有的对小说3要素的认知来画的。</span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"\">而且</span><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">阅读框架不在于多精美，目的只是为了便于理解，就像导航一样，你管它是林志玲还是郭德纲，能指方向就行。</span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"\">框架出来后，阅读方向就清晰了。</span></p><p><br/></p><p><strong style=\"\"><span style=\"\"><strong style=\"\"><span style=\"\"><strong style=\"\">▼</strong></span></strong></span></strong><span style=\"\"><strong style=\"\"><span style=\"\"><strong style=\"\"><span style=\"\"><strong style=\"\"> </strong></span></strong>第三步，第一遍变速阅读</span></strong></span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"\">根据上一步的阅读方向，我花了大约1个小时将<span style=\"\">《小说课》</span>从头到尾翻了一遍，同时更新了阅读框架。</span></p><p><span style=\"\"><br/></span></p><p><img style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: 592px !important; visibility: visible !important;\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/xye473fPuibyWA0OtYRmpQZCcBYpNDqjgpwYFJeYhiaHkcRnV9MBiaJic5H0ibUrANAs1qdltbyc5dpBYgo31eRff9A/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" data-copyright=\"0\" data-ratio=\"0.5077698446031079\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/xye473fPuibyWA0OtYRmpQZCcBYpNDqjgpwYFJeYhiaHkcRnV9MBiaJic5H0ibUrANAs1qdltbyc5dpBYgo31eRff9A/640?wx_fmt=png\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2381\" _width=\"592px\" data-fail=\"0\" data-local=\"false\"/></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"\">因为我知道第一遍变速阅读后，还要做第二遍甚至第三遍的阅读，因此我读起来就比较快了。</span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"\">有些我之前就有所了解的内容</span><span style=\"\">（比如人物和故事的叙述方式）</span><span style=\"\">，我阅读的时候就快速略过了。</span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"\">而故事的情节和小说套路，这部分我之前不清楚，而且跟我的目的强相关，因此我就稍微读得慢些。</span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"\">这么下来，比我以前不管什么内容，都用一个速度看，注意力集中多了。</span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"\">这就好像开车一样，匀速行驶容易疲乏难以坚持；适当变速反而效率更高，更快到达目的地。</span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"\"><strong style=\"\"><span style=\"\"><strong style=\"\"><span style=\"\"><strong style=\"\"><strong style=\"\">▼</strong></strong></span></strong><strong style=\"\"><span style=\"\"><strong style=\"\"><strong style=\"\"> </strong></strong></span></strong>第四步，第二遍重点精读</span></strong></span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"\">第二遍阅读时，我就</span><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">同步做笔记</span><span style=\"\">了。</span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"\">因为书里反复强调，只有归纳到自己的知识体系中，在有需要的时候才能被顺畅调用出来。</span></p><p><span style=\"\"><br/></span></p><p><img style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: 592px !important; visibility: visible !important;\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/xye473fPuibyWA0OtYRmpQZCcBYpNDqjgc040G267BZVEXLQqDWZWSjoQuZlLg6e7NHxwwPC9F0KrWYiadD39OCw/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" data-copyright=\"0\" data-ratio=\"0.42208774583963693\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/xye473fPuibyWA0OtYRmpQZCcBYpNDqjgc040G267BZVEXLQqDWZWSjoQuZlLg6e7NHxwwPC9F0KrWYiadD39OCw/640?wx_fmt=png\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1322\" _width=\"592px\" data-fail=\"0\" data-local=\"false\"/></p><p><span style=\"\">▲ 我略显简陋的OneNote读书笔记</span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"\">经过上面四个步骤读完<span style=\"\">《小说课》</span>后，我基本就清楚写故事的基本方法了。</span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"\">接下来要做的，就是</span><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">学以致用</span><span style=\"\">。</span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"\">《学习力：颠覆职场学习的高效方法》反复跟我强调：<strong style=\"\">任何没有被输出的知识都是无用的。</strong></span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"\">因此，我用制造情节矛盾来推进故事发展的方式，写了一篇颇具阅读性的故事。</span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"\">尝到多重阅读的甜头后，我如法炮制，在OneNote中又搭建了诸如新媒体写作，儿童发展心理学等知识体系。</span></p><p><span style=\"\"><br/></span></p><p><img style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: 204px !important; visibility: visible !important;\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/xye473fPuibyWA0OtYRmpQZCcBYpNDqjgY70iclNScF2pfibTU0ewQqtTEDUswXvic4tbYIH32GuD0y8WqHeibu8gNg/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" data-copyright=\"0\" data-ratio=\"2.607843137254902\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/xye473fPuibyWA0OtYRmpQZCcBYpNDqjgY70iclNScF2pfibTU0ewQqtTEDUswXvic4tbYIH32GuD0y8WqHeibu8gNg/640?wx_fmt=png\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"204\" _width=\"204px\" data-fail=\"0\" data-local=\"false\"/></p><p><span style=\"\">▲ 我搭的知识体系</span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"\">搭了这些知识体系后，我发现我再也不焦虑了，连我的脱发情况也有好转！</span></p><p><span style=\"\"><br/></span></p><p><br/><img style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: 592px !important; visibility: visible !important;\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/xye473fPuibyWA0OtYRmpQZCcBYpNDqjgfEky8flEibdcfkl5nRyhz8xqCvqgreaHpzaZ89psOtQlegY8rKMbocA/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" data-copyright=\"0\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/xye473fPuibyWA0OtYRmpQZCcBYpNDqjgfEky8flEibdcfkl5nRyhz8xqCvqgreaHpzaZ89psOtQlegY8rKMbocA/640?wx_fmt=png\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"640\" _width=\"592px\" data-fail=\"0\" data-local=\"false\"/></p><p> <br/></p><h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"\"><em style=\"\"><span style=\"\"></span></em></span></strong><img src=\"https://ossimg.xinli001.com/20181023/4e4595ffdf5736fa11cedc4c5d7afa30.png?x-oss-process=image/quality,Q_80\"/><strong><span style=\"\"><em style=\"\"><span style=\"\">05</span></em></span></strong></h1><p> </p><p> </p><p><span style=\"\">学习不是比谁睡得少，秃得早，也不是搞虚假努力的自我感动。它跟开车一样，讲究的是技巧和方法。</span></p><p><br/></p><p><strong><span style=\"\">《学习力》这本书，对我最大的价值，就是让以前盲目努力的我，也成了一个有方法的人。</span></strong></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"\">你看，</span><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">有了正确的学习方法，以前满嘴跑大炮的我，也能摇身一变，人模狗样地分享干货讲成功学了，是不是很神奇？</span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"\">所以，想改变命运，就别再转发锦鲤了，毕竟它已自身难保。</span></p><p><span style=\"\"><br/></span></p><p><img style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: 550px !important; visibility: visible !important;\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/xye473fPuibyWA0OtYRmpQZCcBYpNDqjgbicIGqsjDBvBnMLho6lrgibgKfKaR5ubQiaO8bbgbOsId8jcHGS2LuLibQ/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" data-copyright=\"0\" data-ratio=\"0.6345454545454545\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/xye473fPuibyWA0OtYRmpQZCcBYpNDqjgbicIGqsjDBvBnMLho6lrgibgKfKaR5ubQiaO8bbgbOsId8jcHGS2LuLibQ/640?wx_fmt=png\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"550\" _width=\"550px\" data-fail=\"0\" data-local=\"false\"/><br/></p><p><span style=\"\"></span></p><p><strong style=\"\"><span style=\"\">系统性地提升自己的学习能力才是性价比最高的投资！</span></strong></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"\"><strong style=\"\"><span style=\"\"><br/></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"\"><strong style=\"\">——  我是分割线  ——</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"\"><strong style=\"\"><span style=\"\"><br/></span></strong></span></p><p><span style=\"\"><strong style=\"\"><span style=\"\"><br/></span></strong></span></p><p><span style=\"\">看完苗小小同学这篇幽默又带有干货的文章，我想到之前沟通时，她感慨“通过这本书比学过的任何写作课程都有用”。</span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"\">我想这也是这本书的价值，</span><strong style=\"\"><span style=\"\">将底层学习方法应用于自己的工作中，做到更高效、更有价值的产出。</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"\"><br/></span></p><p><strong style=\"\"><span style=\"\">同时也将自身炼化为真正的学习高手。</span></strong></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p>                        </div>\n\n                                                     <div class=\"article-copyright\">\n                                <p>\n                                    <span class=\"subtitle\">原作者名:</span>\n                                    <span class=\"copyright-desc\">作者 / 苗小小</span>\n                                </p>\n                                <p>\n                                    <span class=\"subtitle\">转载来源:</span>\n                                    <span class=\"copyright-desc\">苗小小公众号</span>\n\n                                </p>\n                                <p>\n                                    <span class=\"subtitle\">转载原标题:</span>\n                                    <span class=\"copyright-desc\">无</span>\n                                </p>\n                                <p>\n                                    <span class=\"subtitle\">授权说明:</span>\n                                    <span class=\"copyright-desc\">授权转载</span>\n                                </p>\n                            </div>\n                                          \n                    </div>\n                         <!-- 文章结尾 -->\n                        "]}
